{"tid":1039560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圍牆惹禍】無證婦滋擾侵侵支持者 料被驅逐出境","createTime":"2019-02-27T13:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T14:23:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7444e216357f4f1da49e91495ec971f70706c6","tid":1039560,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）美國一名23歲男子，日前戴著寫有「讓美國再次偉大」的帽子，到麻省度假勝地鱈魚角（Cape Cod）一間墨西哥餐廳消遣，期間遭一名女子騷擾，頭上的帽子一度被她拿下來，有人報警。警方調查後，發現涉案女子的旅遊簽證早已逾期失效，預料她將被遞解出境。<br />\n記者：易珮華<br />\n涉事女子Rosiane Santos現年41歲，祖藉巴西，1994年持旅遊簽證入境美國後一直逾期居留，報稱居於麻省法爾茅斯(Falmouth)。她稱是被男事主所戴的帽子惹怒，認為特朗普既然要起美墨圍牆，他的支持者就沒資格在墨西哥餐廳吃飯，所以才與他發生衝突。<br />\n <br />\n除被控行為不檢，傷人和毆打罪之外，當局又揭發她非法居留，聯邦移民與海關執法局（ICE）已展開相關法律程序，預料她在接受移民法庭審判後，會被遞解出境。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190227/large/1551253164_647d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190227%2Flarge%2F1551253164_647d.jpg&h=219182a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190227/59308452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59308452&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=f8a97a23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59308452&h=ab5fcf41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190227/59308452</a><br />\n<br />\n住得耐得滯唔記得自己係非法移民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14634b8d92b2009b99ade0e6cfb8d34cbbfa7922","tid":1039560,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"0e7444e216357f4f1da49e91495ec971f70706c6","tid":1039560,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）美國一名23歲男子，日前戴著寫有「讓美國再次偉大」的帽子，到麻省度假勝地鱈魚角（Cape Cod）一間墨西哥餐廳消遣，期間遭一名女子騷擾，頭上的帽子一度被她拿下來，有人報警。警方調查後，發現涉案女子的旅遊簽證早已逾期失效，預料她將被遞解出境。<br />\n記者：易珮華<br />\n涉事女子Rosiane Santos現年41歲，祖藉巴西，1994年持旅遊簽證入境美國後一直逾期居留，報稱居於麻省法爾茅斯(Falmouth)。她稱是被男事主所戴的帽子惹怒，認為特朗普既然要起美墨圍牆，他的支持者就沒資格在墨西哥餐廳吃飯，所以才與他發生衝突。<br />\n <br />\n除被控行為不檢，傷人和毆打罪之外，當局又揭發她非法居留，聯邦移民與海關執法局（ICE）已展開相關法律程序，預料她在接受移民法庭審判後，會被遞解出境。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190227/large/1551253164_647d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190227%2Flarge%2F1551253164_647d.jpg&h=219182a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190227/59308452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59308452&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=f8a97a23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59308452&h=ab5fcf41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190227/59308452</a><br />\n<br />\n住得耐得滯唔記得自己係非法移民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主客不分<br />\n雀巢鳩佔"},{"pid":"4f409fbbd7732cc09bd059116efbd332f2dd2c42","tid":1039560,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"邏輯好奇怪<br />\n其實兩者有乜關系？"},{"pid":"1a9fe68b8bb288511dd049f472b43a762b3c912f","tid":1039560,"uid":113626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"非法移民=美國民主黨d fd=賣國賊"},{"pid":"6fa315413d888fe6abc46f21001f1534a5d1390a","tid":1039560,"uid":4525,"like":6,"